n<br />\n想送出親手設計既腦魔聖誕卡畀大家<br />\n<br />\n實物圖如下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/7bc5a771e0262f38530c45a6ed6e1b9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F7bc5a771e0262f38530c45a6ed6e1b9a.jpg&h=0a68009f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意:<br />\n1. 第二回，只寄香港境內<br />\n2. CD-R填左都無用 要係呢個post 留名先會寄出<br />\n3. 張卡類似post既型式 (唔會有信封)<br />\n4. 第一回填過既巴絲打唔洗再填，你地一定有<br />\n5. 如果第一回已經有既巴絲打，唔好貪心，留啲溫暖畀有需要既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想要既請先留名及進入下面既Link 填入你既資料<br />\n<br />\n聖誕卡會在十二月中寄出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/5vgZ3A1xXJjzwTcG2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F5vgZ3A1xXJjzwTcG2&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B83vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=02a585c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/5vgZ3A1xXJjzwTcG2</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好靚 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90319f934901c549ee625b4799706aa27534b663","tid":19712,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c92f0a0f32dbfcf5d50a1baa334f5f497bb673dd","tid":19712,"uid":3195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打寫低回郵地址我會寫返比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57faf775ca922844afb9a0f33c1075c4ee7b1d01","tid":19712,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:20:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"325786ccbfe57ab736cca306b52fdf6011f8fe9d","tid":19712,"uid":14479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"留名